3 - bedroom apartment - 101.4m basic rent 20 million/month, full 22 - 25 million/month.

All apartments have free service until the end of 2025.
The building is fully equipped and the apartments have comfortable parking slots (1 extra basement).
Apartment prices include taxes and are paid monthly.
